Class BaseManager

Direct Known Subclasses:
BlockManager
public abstract class BaseManager
extends java.lang.Object

This is a queue that accepts objects and processes these objects. A user will create and instance of the EventHandler and pass it into this event collector. Subclasses include an Ordered and Parallel Event version for when the objects are visitors to a common handler, and Ordered Block version for when the common held object visits each queue item.
